               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350817-name-1126" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-1126" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-1126" type="surname" value="DODDS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-1126" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM DODDS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at West-ham. On the 5th of August I went in my chaise to Highbury-park and I left my choise, with my coat in it, in care of a boy—I received information, and came out—I missed my coat—I afterwards saw it—here it is.</p>
               <p>
